\subsection{Time}\label{time}

Trips are more frequent during the winter, which corresponds to the
months where trips are most likely to be successful. However, the
relationship with CPUE and month is less direct, which is highest in the
late fall and in January. Trips are most frequent on Mondays and drop
drastically on Fridays and Saturdays. The distribution of trip returns
range from 11 am to midnight, with peaks times of 1 pm and 7 pm.

